<div class="container">
  <!-- Example row of columns -->
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4 component-case-box">
      <h3>1. Greeting</h3>

      <h4>Basic render</h4>
      {{1-greeting name="Joseph"}}

      <h4>Two parameters</h4>
      {{1-greeting name="Anne" salutation="Welcome"}}

      <h4>Flashy greeting</h4>
      {{1-greeting name="Paul" salutation="Welcome" flash=true}}

      <h4>Block Message</h4>
      {{#1-greeting name="Andy"}}
        I'm very happy you're here. I hope you enjoy your stay in Guatemala.
      {{/1-greeting}}

    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4 component-case-box">
      <h3>2. Secret Message</h3>

      <h4>Toggle when no password is required</h4>
      {{#2-secret-message title="Atlantis location"}}
        Location hypotheses of Atlantis are various proposed real-world settings for the legendary island of Atlantis, described as a lost civilization mentioned in Plato's dialogues.
      {{/2-secret-message}}

      <h4>Show password input</h4>
      {{#2-secret-message title="Atlantis location" passwordRequired=true onAuthorize=(action 'authorizeOpen')}}
        Location hypotheses of Atlantis are various proposed real-world settings for the legendary island of Atlantis, described as a lost civilization mentioned in Plato's dialogues.
      {{/2-secret-message}}

      <h4>Send authorize action</h4>
      {{#2-secret-message title="Atlantis location" passwordRequired=true onAuthorize=(action 'authorizeOpen')}}
        Location hypotheses of Atlantis are various proposed real-world settings for the legendary island of Atlantis, described as a lost civilization mentioned in Plato's dialogues.
      {{/2-secret-message}}

      <h4>Open correctly</h4>
      {{#2-secret-message title="Atlantis location" passwordRequired=true onAuthorize=(action 'authorizeOpen')}}
        Location hypotheses of Atlantis are various proposed real-world settings for the legendary island of Atlantis, described as a lost civilization mentioned in Plato's dialogues.
      {{/2-secret-message}}

      <h4>Show error state</h4>
      {{#2-secret-message title="Atlantis location" passwordRequired=true onAuthorize=(action 'authorizeOpen')}}
        Location hypotheses of Atlantis are various proposed real-world settings for the legendary island of Atlantis, described as a lost civilization mentioned in Plato's dialogues.
      {{/2-secret-message}}

      <h4>Error status is cleared on input update</h4>
      {{#2-secret-message title="Atlantis location" passwordRequired=true onAuthorize=(action 'authorizeOpen')}}
        Location hypotheses of Atlantis are various proposed real-world settings for the legendary island of Atlantis, described as a lost civilization mentioned in Plato's dialogues.
      {{/2-secret-message}}
   </div>
    <div class="col-md-4 component-case-box">
      <h3>3. Login form</h3>
      <h4>Login form</h4>
      {{3-login-form}}
      <p>Login rule: <br> <em>password === username</em></p>

      <br>
      {{3-login-form}}
      <br>
      <h4>Displays form when not authenticated</h4>
      <h4>Shakes when login is incorrect and password is cleared</h4>
      <h4>Displays message with username when authenticated</h4>
      <h4>Shakes when login is incorrect twice</h4>
      <h4>Logout button unauthenticates the user and shows form</h4>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
